title: Episode 25: How many, how manyyyy?
itunes:title: Episode 25: How many, how manyyyy?
description:
Bobby angers a table of 12 Orange County mothers.

Khalyla feels adequately loved but under-desired.

Gilbert is Dr. Nothing.

We reveal Bobby's blood test results, challenge each others' IQs, and get mean about hashtags.

Sorry, we're just a bunch of stupid children.

#TheUnitedStatesofAmerica #tears

 

Recorded January 18, 2016

Music by Bobby Lee

Instagram: @tigerbelly

Twitter: @thetigerbelly

www.thetigerbelly.com
